{"tid":2194373,"cid":5,"subCid":10,"title":"★支app Game被禁 印度學生不能玩 PUBG 上吊自盡","createTime":"2020-09-08T12:45:14.000Z","updateTime":"2020-09-10T16:56:34.000Z","uid":19454,"like":34,"dislike":1,"uniUserReply":18,"replies":[{"pid":"2ebdd74a7d2fa9a70c7318cdecd7be013c27de56","tid":2194373,"uid":19454,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2020-09-08T12:45:14.000Z","msg":"印度信息技術部於當地時間 9 月 2 日以「有損印度主權與完整、印度國防、國家安全與公共秩序」為由，禁止中國的 118 款手機 App，其中包括一款大逃殺遊戲「絕地求生」。而一名 21 歲學生因無法繼續玩遊戲而選擇上吊自盡。<br />\n<br />\n據印度媒體報道，一名 21 歲學生因政府禁止中國的手機 App 而無法繼續玩大逃殺遊戲「絕地求生」，被發現在家中選擇上吊自盡。據該名學生的母親指，兒子在吃過早餐後便回到自己房間，而當她叫兒子吃午餐，但敲了數次兒子也未有應門時，母親把鄰居叫來並衝進房間，發現兒子已經上吊自盡。<br />\n<br />\n <br />\n<br />\n而該名學生的母親續稱，兒子平日晚上會玩「絕地求生」作消閒，相信兒子是因無法繼續玩遊戲而感到沮喪，繼而自盡。警方聽後亦表示現時遊戲被禁或是導致他自盡的原因。<br />\n<a href=\"https://unwire.hk/2020/09/08/india-21-year-old-student-die-by-suicide-because-of-india-banning-the-game-pubg/life-tech/\" data-sr-url=\"https://r.lihkg.com/link?u=https%3A%2F%2Funwire.hk%2F2020%2F09%2F08%2Findia-21-year-old-student-die-by-suicide-because-of-india-banning-the-game-pubg%2Flife-tech%2F&d=pZTDRaRh7CFw%2FURiZY0DNRSC%2F35X4DTIU%2BW3we%2FDSDs%3D&h=0d93e907\" data-auto-link target=\"_blank\">https://unwire.hk/2020/09/08/india-21-year-old-student-die-by-suicide-because-of-india-banning-the-game-pubg/life-tech/</a>"},{"pid":"2552e03db8fc4c9bdf88fa647ec5af54a08f556a","tid":2194373,"uid":301989,"like":29,"dislike":0,"score":29,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2020-09-08T12:45:44.000Z","msg":"on9仔<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/sosad.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/sosad.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/sosad.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"a4fd88f52e556d17c79ea4e22d1cbf5ceedf496a","tid":2194373,"uid":347528,"like":7,"dislike":1,"score":6,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2020-09-08T12:46:05.000Z","msg":"支那害人地仔女<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/angry.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/angry.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><img src=\"/assets/faces/